{"tid":205293,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"4 月 18 係 坤 哥 既 生 日 呀","createTime":"2017-04-17T16:21:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T04:03:03.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47b251ae49d2e2be1e5cd5a14475f89bf947f150","tid":205293,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T16:21:29.000Z","msg":"吳業坤（James Ng Yip Kwan，1990年4月18日－），香港歌手及演員，現為TVB經理人合約藝員，成為TVB力捧新晉小生之一。他憑2010年參加歌唱比賽節目《超級巨聲2》獲得第五名，由此踏上星途。<br />\n從出道以來都想當一名歌手，唯一直沒能得到這個機會，經過五年在無綫電視擔當演員後，終於在2015年簽約加盟星娛樂唱片公司，並憑歌曲《原來她不夠愛我》和《陽光點的歌》有人記得，並曾經奪得「叱咤樂壇我最喜愛的歌曲大獎」和兩度奪得「叱咤樂壇我最喜愛的男歌手」獎項。代表作除了《原來她不夠愛我》和《陽光點的歌》兩首後，也包括2016年推出的三台冠軍歌曲《百姓》。<br />\n<br />\n既然坤哥之前咁想做SITA<br />\n就希望佢可以好似SITA咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c21fd705cc1eac2ffba85d83936987e9c0ff5e9","tid":205293,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T00:25:59.000Z","msg":"祝佢仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e16a993b19f21444734310b1db3aaf56b0ecc014","tid":205293,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T00:26:42.000Z","msg":"祝坤哥生日快樂"},{"pid":"1d18be8e0d48aec230202ddaabc05d55f67c93d4","tid":205293,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T00:28:47.000Z","msg":"關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"fb24a4fbab08da466e42ab357806943b0be82097","tid":205293,"uid":58249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T00:29:27.000Z","msg":"仲未死？"},{"pid":"ad9c9a07cc2010068b51c8172449e24f919437aa","tid":205293,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T00:33:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祝佢仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p